    "description": "<p>\r\n\tTHE WORLD MANAGEMENT PTE LTD</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>The World Management</strong> was established in 1983. Over the years, we have developed a niche in the area of office automation for accounting, internal co-ordination and external communications. TWM is a premier qualified solution provider for <strong>Sage 300 ERP </strong>(<strong>ACCPAC)</strong> and <strong>SAP</strong><strong> Business One</strong>. Our company also specializes in office total solution consultation. Over the years, we have won a pool of customer ranging from sole proprietor business to national corporations with our qualified product and services. Having a pool of loyal supporters, we constantly seek advancement and in search of new innovations to provide service excellence to our clients.</p>\r\n",
